        <h2><i class="fas fa-bars"></i> Navigation & UI</h2>
        <div class="test-grid">
          <div class="test-card">
            <h3><span class="status-indicator status-working"></span>Responsive Design</h3>
            <p>Modern, responsive design that works on all devices.</p>
            <div class="feature-list">
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i>Mobile responsive</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i>Modern UI design</li>
